the early stages of the season in rio resulting in a broken foot and ankle forced blundell to miss several races despite this mark was third in the rookie standings with three top six finishes in the us  detroit grand prix and michigan international speedway races  was a breakout year blundell came within one corner of winning the detroit belle isle grand prix before running out of fuel an event he described at the time as the worst disappointment of his career in the very next race he powered past gil de ferran on the final straight to win the grand prix of portland by  seconds blundell recorded further race victories in toronto and fontana en route to sixth in the championship that year he was also named british driver of the year by autosport magazine  was not a year for the books and a massive crash early in  left him to languish at the bottom of the table he returned to pacwest for a final season in  however another disappointing season –  pts st overall – lead to a mutual split with pacwest racing from driving to commentatingedit blundell again crossed the atlantic to focus on his sports car racing he failed to finish le mans with the mg lola team though he and his teammates impressed offtrack blundell joined itv television in britain as an analyst for the  formula one season this position lasted until the end of the  formula one season when itv lost coverage to the bbc since  blundells racing involvement has steadily declined with only the occasional event he did test a dale coyne champ car to help prepare darren manning for a oneoff in the first cart race in britain at rockingham and raced in the british round of the world rally championship  saw great success in sports cars along with johnny herbert and david brabham he finished second at the  hours of le mans completing a – sweep by bentley he also finished third at the  hours of sebring finishing top among the bentleys blundell also spends time running a management company mb partners who handle the contracts of such people as mclaren test driver gary paffett and british formula  champion and indycar driver mike conway the name refers to the fact that it was founded by blundell and former teammate martin brundle who stepped down from the company in january  in a newspaper article in  blundell was openly critical of oval racing in general and of the  izod indycar world championship which had claimed the life of dan wheldon helmetedit blundells helmet is yellow with three red stripes and two yellow gaps in the middle a blue stripe in the entire chin area and a blue circle on the top with his golden initials on it the rear of his helmet bears the motto the will to win  a quote from his grandfather racing recordedit complete international formula  resultsedit key races in bold indicate pole position races in italics indicate fastest lap year entrant            dc points  fleetray racing sil ret val  spa  pau don  brh  bir dnq th  bs automotive per  imo ret bug ret jar   lola motorsport jer  val  pau ret sil  mnz ret per ret brh  bir ret bug  zol  dij ret th   middlebridge sil  val ret pau  jer dnq per ret brh ret bir  spa dns bug ret dij  th  complete japanese formula  championship resultsedit key races in bold indicate pole position races in italics indicate fastest lap year entrant         dc points  footwork racing international suz fuj min suz sug fuj suz suz ret nc  complete  hours of le mans resultsedit year team codrivers car class laps pos class pos  nissan motorsports julian bailey martin donnelly nissan rc c  dnf dnf  nissan motorsports international julian bailey gianfranco brancatelli nissan rck c  dnf dnf  peugeot talbot sport derek warwick yannick dalmas peugeot  evo b c  st st  gtc gulf racing ray bellm maurizio sandro sala mclaren f gtr gt  th rd  mg sport  racing ltd julian bailey kevin mcgarrity mglola ex lmp  dnf dnf  mg sport  racing ltd julian bailey kevin mcgarrity mglola ex lmp  dnf dnf  team bentley david brabham johnny herbert bentley speed  lmg