ccasional event he did test a dale coyne champ car to help prepare darren manning for a oneoff in the first cart race in britain at rockingham and raced in the british round of the world rally championship  saw great success in sports cars along with johnny herbert and david brabham he finished second at the  hours of le mans completing a – sweep by bentley he also finished third at the  hours of sebring finishing top among the bentleys blundell also spends time running a management company mb partners who handle the contracts of such people as mclaren test driver gary paffett and british formula  champion and indycar driver mike conway the name refers to the fact that it was founded by blundell and former teammate martin brundle who stepped down from the company in january  in a newspaper article in  blundell was openly critical of oval racing in general and of the  izod indycar world championship which had claimed the life of dan wheldon helmetedit blundells helmet is yellow with three red stripes and two yellow gaps in the middle a blue stripe in the entire chin area and a blue circle on the top with his golden initials on it the rear of his helmet bears the motto the will to win  a quote from his grandfather racing recordedit complete international formula  resultsedit key races in bold indicate pole position races in italics indicate fastest lap year entrant            dc points  fleetray racing sil ret val  spa  pau don  brh  bir dnq th  bs automotive per  imo ret bug ret jar   lola motorsport jer  val  pau ret sil  mnz ret per ret brh  bir ret bug  zol  dij ret th   middlebridge sil  val ret pau  jer dnq per ret brh ret bir  spa dns bug ret dij  th  complete japanese formula  championship resultsedit key races in bold indicate pole position races in italics indicate fastest lap year entrant         dc points  footwork racing international suz fuj min suz sug fuj suz suz ret nc  complete  hours of le mans resultsedit year team codrivers car class laps pos clas