sor for young driver philip glew glew competed in the  avon junior formula ford championship and is a close family friend in  mark blundell had an expanded mg programme which included a run in the british round of the world rally championship in addition to a regular studio expert role with itv’s formula one coverage and regular presenter duties for carlton television’s pulling power series from  mark concentrated more and more on his tv career as well as launching mb sports management ltd with martin brundle – a new driver management company offtrack mark blundell joined itv television in britain as an analyst during the formula one season this position lasted until the end of the  formula one season when itv lost coverage to the bbc mb sports management ltd has since gone from strength to strength and now represents a number of drivers including the likes of gary paffett mike conway and tim bridgman book mark blundell now for celebrity appearances through celebrity group your shortlist submit shortlist ↗ print this shortlist ↗ first name surname direct phone office number mobile phone email best time to contact you to discuss please provide as much information as possible a brief description of your requirements please list here any specific talent in which you are interested or a general description of your ideal talent such as london based motor racing enthusiast must be under  or yummy mummy etc talent wish list we realise this information is sometimes confidential however we need market sector as a minimum such as automotive cosmetic supermarket product gambling etc name of client product or service please specify maximum budget in euros £ or us for talent a for shoot b for media usage or for an event such as a personal appearance maximum proposed budget for example asda mums teenage boys car drivers frequent holiday makers afluent males  target marketdemographic if your enquiry is for a tvc or other media campaign please specify the territory where this will 